<P><STRONG>SimpleDraw</STRONG> is sample C code illustrating the use of =
OpenGL.=20
&nbsp; It is intended to accompany the book <EM><STRONG>3D Computer =
Graphics: A=20
mathematical approach with OpenGL</STRONG>, </EM>by S. Buss, Cambridge=20
University Press, 2003. &nbsp; However, it can be used independently as=20
well.</P>
<P><STRONG>SimpleDraw </STRONG>shows how to draw points, lines, line =
strips and=20
line loops.&nbsp;&nbsp; It consists of two source files,=20
<STRONG>SimpleDraw.c</STRONG> and =
<STRONG>SimpleDraw.h.</STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;=20
